Public Domain, Anyone Can do Whatever they want, there is no protection of IP and you do not need to ask. Feel free to use parts of code in your project, make small versions and release them, make major changes and release them, or whatever you wish. Our first priority is the overal playerbase and individual liberties. Credit back to us would be nice, but is not necessary.

